# Proposals

This directory indexes design-in-progress for `<repo-name>`.

## Belongs Here

- proposed documentation structure changes
- alternative placements and naming options
- open design questions and tradeoffs

## Does Not Belong Here

- current canonical guidance: `../Architecture/`
- adopted decisions and rationale: `../Decisions/`
- migration rollout records: `../Migrations/`
- retired material: `../Archive/`

## Use

Use this subtree for work that is still under consideration.
